```

---

#### **requirements-dev.txt** (691 bytes)
**What it does**: Lists development-only dependencies
**Includes**:
- Everything in requirements.txt
- Testing tools (pytest)
- Code formatting (black, flake8)
- Documentation tools (Sphinx)

**When to use**:
```bash
